title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-20-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show AUG-20-2013 TUES








The Glenn Beck Program - 08/20/13 







The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,


Glenn and the guys discuss a variety of topics.

 How is it that Bill Kristol is just NOW realizing that the Muslim Brotherhood is bad?

 Also, discusses the shocking letter a woman wrote to the parent of an autistic child,
  telling them to euthanize them.

 And Al Jazeera America is now available across the US.

 The guys discuss this, plus the mother of the molested child in Michigan joins Glenn.

 Plus a dead body removed form Olivia Newton John's house.
